TITLE: Implementing Database Sessions with Custom SessionStore
DESCRIPTION: Example of implementing a custom session store to persist user sessions in a database instead of cookies. This requires implementing get, set, delete, and optionally deleteByLogoutToken methods for session management.
SOURCE: https://github.com/auth0/nextjs-auth0/blob/main/EXAMPLES.md#2025-04-19_snippet_20

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
export const auth0 = new Auth0Client({
  sessionStore: {
    async get(id) {
